  "detailed_description": "Mini Healer is an MMO inspired RPG where you play as the healer in a party and challenge various bosses in the dungeon. Added with ARPG inspired loot system and deep character customization.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/955740/extras/171dc55af01f330f956c9761d0aa6533.poster.avif?t=1663800026\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/955740/extras/171dc55af01f330f956c9761d0aa6533.webm?t=1663800026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/955740/extras/171dc55af01f330f956c9761d0aa6533.mp4?t=1663800026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>35 unique bosses to challenge<br></li><li>Over 300 unique artifacts to collect<br></li><li>Over 23 spells to customize<br></li><li>In-depth skill trees with 3 classes and over 100 nodes<br></li><li>In-depth Crafting system to upgrade and modify artifacts collected<br></li><li>Over 150 achievement bonuses to collect<br></li><li>Simple procedurally generated end game dungeons</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/955740/extras/8658860dbd0c1c8827d9ecbc485c87da.poster.avif?t=1663800026\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/955740/extras/8658860dbd0c1c8827d9ecbc485c87da.webm?t=1663800026\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/955740/extras/8658860dbd0c1c8827d9ecbc485c87da.mp4?t=1663800026\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you liked the game or have feedback you can always join the <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn